    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>MASTER MAYAN COMBAT:</strong></h2>As the Nacom, a revered Mayan warrior, skill and strategy are paramount. Engage in a combat system that rewards precision and timing:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859940/extras/5d97a6225604e22038fe4164e5869208.poster.avif?t=1692407063\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859940/extras/5d97a6225604e22038fe4164e5869208.webm?t=1692407063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859940/extras/5d97a6225604e22038fe4164e5869208.mp4?t=1692407063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Versatile Weaponry:</strong> Each weapon comes with its unique combo sequences, offering different strategies for every confrontation.<br><strong><br>Weapon Evolution:</strong> Progress from the basic Flint-tipped weapons to the sharper Obsidian edges, advance to the mystical properties of Enchanted Jade, and culminate your journey with the powerful Steel blades.<br><br><strong><br>Mighty Blood Magic:</strong> Utilize Blood to cast intense spells, gathered from vanquishing foes or the brave Sacrifice Spell.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859940/extras/8021d51bd2c9bbd186ba05eebf372adc.poster.avif?t=1692407063\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859940/extras/8021d51bd2c9bbd186ba05eebf372adc.webm?t=1692407063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859940/extras/8021d51bd2c9bbd186ba05eebf372adc.mp4?t=1692407063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Defensive Mastery:</strong> Whether you choose to dodge with rolls, parry to stun, block impending doom, or seize the moment with a counter, defense is as crucial as offense.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859940/extras/9e4a941624c06e61b12a568e146f30ad.poster.avif?t=1692407063\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859940/extras/9e4a941624c06e61b12a568e146f30ad.webm?t=1692407063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859940/extras/9e4a941624c06e61b12a568e146f30ad.mp4?t=1692407063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>JOURNEY THROUGH MESOAMERICA:</strong></h2><br><strong>Traverse an expansive grid-coordinate map and carve your path:</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859940/extras/cd9ce0d557624bfecf3cc96e7c44c7d2.poster.avif?t=1692407063\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859940/extras/cd9ce0d557624bfecf3cc96e7c44c7d2.webm?t=1692407063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859940/extras/cd9ce0d557624bfecf3cc96e7c44c7d2.mp4?t=1692407063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Campaign Map: </strong>The choice is yours: pursue the main quest or embark on side adventures. Beware of enemy interceptors leading to Skirmish Maps, bringing an open-world flavor to your journey.<br><br><strong>Strategic Centers:</strong><br><br><strong>Temple: </strong>Seek out potent spells, weapons, and enhancements.<br><br><strong>Armory:</strong> Refresh and upgrade your tools of battle.<br><br><strong>Barracks: </strong>Before each challenge, ensure your loadout matches the task at hand.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859940/extras/6bfeaf9bda533aebb79b8e3744fbc428.poster.avif?t=1692407063\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859940/extras/6bfeaf9bda533aebb79b8e3744fbc428.webm?t=1692407063\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1859940/extras/6bfeaf9bda533aebb79b8e3744fbc428.mp4?t=1692407063\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
